    • wrap

      public static Hidden wrap(Element element)
      Creates a Hidden widget that wraps an existing <input type='hidden'> element. This element must already be attached to the document. If the element is removed from the document, you must call Widget.removeFromParent().
      Parameters:
      element - the element to be wrapped
